<topic xml:id="openwebui-setting-model-system-prompt"
 role="task" xml:lang="en"
 xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.2"
 xmlns:its="http://www.w3.org/2005/11/its"
 xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
 xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
 xmlns:trans="http://docbook.org/ns/transclusion">
  <info>
    <title>Setting the default system prompt for an AI model</title>
    <meta name="maintainer" content="tbazant@suse.com" its:translate="no"/>
    <abstract>
      <para>
        This topic explains how to set the default system prompt for an AI
        model. The system prompt is then used for new chats if not overridden by
        specifying a system prompt for a user or a chat.
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </info>
  <procedure>
    <itemizedlist>
      <title>Requirements</title>
      <xi:include href="../snippets/openwebui-requirement-admin-privileges.xml"/>
    </itemizedlist>
    <step>
      <para>
        In the &openwebui; interface, click <guimenu>Workspace</guimenu> in the
        upper part of the left panel.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Select <guimenu>Models</guimenu> in the top menu and scroll to the AI
        model whose system prompt you want to set. Use the pager at the bottom
        if the model is not listed on the current screen.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Click the corresponding pen icon at its right to open the dialog for
        editing the model.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        In the <guimenu>Model Params</guimenu> section, specify the system
        prompt in the <guimenu>System prompt</guimenu> field.
      </para>
      <figure>
        <title>Model system prompt</title>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject role="fo">
            <imagedata fileref="openwebui-workspace-models-sysprompt.png" width="50%"/>
          </imageobject>
          <imageobject role="html">
            <imagedata fileref="openwebui-workspace-models-sysprompt.png" width="50%"/>
          </imageobject>
          <textobject role="description"><phrase>Model system prompt</phrase>
          </textobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </figure>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Confirm with <guimenu>Save &amp; Update</guimenu>.
      </para>
    </step>
  </procedure>
  <section xml:id="ai-model-sysprompt-moreinfo">
    <title>For more information</title>
    <para>
      Find more details about system prompts in
      <link xlink:href="https://documentation.suse.com/suse-ai/1.0/html/AI-system-prompts/index.html"/>.
    </para>
  </section>
</topic>
